Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.35,0:00:42.13,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,不死樹
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.21,0:00:43.62,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\c&HE8EACD&}何為真相
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.62,0:00:44.66,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,何為真相
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.92,0:00:47.21,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,我將成為真相
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.21,0:00:48.63,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\c&HE8EACD&}我將成為真相
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.18,0:00:59.60,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,我看到那片光亮
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.56,0:01:03.56,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\c&HE8EACD&}這就是我的全部
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.56,0:01:05.89,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,這就是我的全部
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.62,0:01:08.38,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.61,0:01:09.40,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,我知道
